M|references|**Keywords:**
M|references|- Exact match: [keyword] — most precise, lower volume
M|references|- Phrase match: "keyword" — moderate precision and volume
M|references|- Broad match: keyword — highest volume, use with smart bidding
M|references|**Audience layering:**
M|references|- Add audiences in "observation" mode first
M|references|- Analyze performance by audience
M|references|- Switch to "targeting" mode for high performers
M|references|**RLSA (Remarketing Lists for Search Ads):**
M|references|- Bid higher on past visitors searching your terms
M|references|- Show different ads to returning searchers
M|references|- Exclude converters from prospecting cg
M|references|**Custom intent audiences:**
M|references|- Based on recent search behavior
M|references|- Create from your converting keywords
M|references|- High intent, good for prospecting
M|references|**In-market audiences:**
M|references|- People actively researching solutions
M|references|- Pre-built by Google
M|references|- Layer with demographics for precision
M|references|**Affinity audiences:**
M|references|- Based on interests and habits
M|references|- Better for awareness
M|references|- Broad but can exclude irrelevant
M|references|**Customer match:**
M|references|- Upload email lists
M|references|- Retarget existing customers
M|references|- Create lookalikes from best customers
M|references|**Similar/lookalike audiences:**
M|references|- Based on your customer match lists
M|references|- Expand reach while maintaining relevance
M|references|- Best when source list is high-quality customers
M|references|**Interest targeting tips:**
M|references|- Layer interests with AND logic for precision
M|references|- Use Audience Insights to research interests
M|references|- Start broad, let algorithm optimize
M|references|- Exclude existing customers always
M|references|**Demographic targeting:**
M|references|- Age and gender (if product-specific)
M|references|- Location (down to zip/postal code)
M|references|- Language
M|references|- Education and work (limited data now)
