M|references|- App installers
M|references|- In-app events
M|references|- Purchase events
M|references|**Source audience quality matters:**
M|references|- Use high-LTV customers, not all customers
M|references|- Purchasers > leads > all visitors
M|references|- Minimum 100 source users, ideally 1,000+
M|references|**Size recommendations:**
M|references|- 1% — most similar, smallest reach
M|references|- 1-3% — good balance for most
M|references|- 3-5% — broader, good for scale
M|references|- 5-10% — very broad, awareness only
M|references|**Layering strategies:**
M|references|- Lookalike + interest = more precision early
M|references|- Test lookalike-only as you scale
M|references|- Exclude the source audience
